# 03 - Asset Inventory

## Purpose

The Asset Inventory identifies information assets within the scope of the Information Security Management System (ISMS).

## Supporting Documentation

* Asset-Register.xlsx

## Asset Categories

* Hardware
* Software
* Cloud Services
* Databases
* Documentation
* Network Infrastructure

## Classification Levels

* Public
* Internal
* Confidential
* Restricted

## Ownership

Each asset is assigned an owner responsible for maintaining appropriate security controls and ensuring compliance with organizational policies.

## Review Frequency

Annually or upon significant business or technology changes.

